name: 西住しほnishizumi shiho(girls and panzer)
description:
based on anime.

She has many official arts that with alternate costumes. I add some and you can see some of them in the examples. This makes her characteristics unstable. If you find something lost just use the prompt to let it back. If you want only the black suit version of her just use the prompt "normal" and put "alternate costume" in negative. Vice versa.

The hardest part is her puffy eyes. Stable diffusion is not able to identify this thus I cannot make it available in this version. If I have time I will make an alternative version of this.

All the examples are generated by hires fix. AOM3 is used as model
